LeBron, on finishing second in MVP voting:<br />
<br />
&quot;It pissed me off. That's my true answer. It pissed me off because out of 101 votes, I got 16 first place votes. That's what pissed me off more than anything. Not saying the winner wasn't deserving or anything, but that pissed me off.&quot;

